data.title: Clownhouse Muzik
data.meta_description: Clownhouse Muzik is a pioneering Chicago-based dance label founded in 1997. With a focus on footwork and juke music, the label has released some of the top dance producers in Chicago, including DJ Thadz, DJ Solo, DJ Spinn, DJ Rashad, and many more. Clownhouse Muzik has played a significant role in shaping the Chicago dance music scene and has continued to push the boundaries of footwork and juke music over the years. With a rich history of innovative releases and influential artists, Clownhouse Muzik remains a vital force in the world of dance music today.
data.text: Clownhouse Muzik is a pioneering Chicago-based dance label founded in 1997.
